:\"data\";s:2428:\"\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2023/08/saigon-wp-meetup-082023.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"577\" src=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2023/08/saigon-wp-meetup-082023-1024x577.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1089\" srcset=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2023/08/saigon-wp-meetup-082023-1024x577.png 1024w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2023/08/saigon-wp-meetup-082023-300x169.png 300w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2023/08/saigon-wp-meetup-082023-768x433.png 768w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2023/08/saigon-wp-meetup-082023-1536x865.png 1536w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2023/08/saigon-wp-meetup-082023.png 1640w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Vào ngày 19.08.2023 tới đây, những người yêu thích WordPress tại Sài Gòn sẽ cùng nhau gặp gỡ và chia sẻ về các chủ đề thú vị.</p>\n\n\n\n<span id=\"more-1088\"></span>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Thời gian</h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>13:30 &#8211; 17:30</strong> ngày <strong>19.08.2023</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Địa điểm</h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>8 Trần Quang Diệu, phường 14, quận 3, TP. HCM</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Nội dung thảo luận</h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Chủ đề 1: Tối ưu tốc độ website WordPress</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Khôi Nguyễn</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Founder/CEO <strong><a href=\"https://codetot.vn/ve-code-tot/\">Code Tốt</a></strong><br>CTO <strong>Nhà Phố Net</strong><br>Locale Manager tại <strong>WordPress tiếng Việt</strong><br>Admin nhóm <strong><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/toiuuweb\">Tối ưu Web</a></strong></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Đăng ký tham gia Meetup</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Bạn vào nhóm Zalo <a href=\"https://zalo.me/g/hblyng586\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://zalo.me/g/hblyng586\">WordPress Meetup Sài Gòn</a> để vote chủ đề yêu thích.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Đơn vị tài trợ và đồng hành</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https://123host.vn\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://123host.vn\">123Host</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://interdata.vn/\">InterData</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://vietnix.vn/\">Vietnix</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Giải Pháp SEO</li>\n\n\n\n<li>In Hương Giang</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"https://vi.wordpress.org/2023/08/02/sai-gon-wordpress-meetup-08-2023/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:30:\"com-wordpress:feed-additions:1\";a:1:{s:7:\"post-id\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"1088\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:38:\"Online Meetup Nha Trang tháng 08.2023\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"https://vi.wordpress.org/2023/08/02/online-meetup-nha-trang-thang-08-2023/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a